### Inventory Management System - API Testing

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1

### ==================== ITEM ENDPOINTS ====================

### Create a new item with initial stock
POST {{baseUrl}}/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "item": {
    "name": "Wireless Headphones",
    "sku": "HEAD-001",
    "description": "Premium wireless headphones with noise cancellation",
    "basePrice": 149.99
  },
  "stock": {
    "quantity": 75,
    "reserved": 0,
    "reorderLevel": 20
  }
}

### Get all items
GET {{baseUrl}}/items

### Get item by ID (replace {id} with actual ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/items/1

### Get item by SKU
GET {{baseUrl}}/items/sku/TSHIRT-001

### Update item
PUT {{baseUrl}}/items/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Classic Cotton T-Shirt",
  "basePrice": 24.99
}

### Check if item is in stock
GET {{baseUrl}}/items/1/in-stock

### Reserve stock for an item
POST {{baseUrl}}/items/1/reserve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 10
}

### Release reserved stock
POST {{baseUrl}}/items/1/release-reserved
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 5
}

### Deduct stock (actual sale)
POST {{baseUrl}}/items/1/deduct
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 3
}

### Add stock (restock)
POST {{baseUrl}}/items/1/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 25
}

### Delete item
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/items/1

### ==================== ITEM VARIANT ENDPOINTS ====================

### Create a variant for an item
POST {{baseUrl}}/items/1/variants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variant": {
    "name": "Black Large T-Shirt",
    "color": "Black",
    "size": "L",
    "description": "Large size in black",
    "price": 19.99
  },
  "stock": {
    "quantity": 35,
    "reserved": 0,
    "reorderLevel": 8
  }
}

### Get all variants of an item
GET {{baseUrl}}/items/1/variants

### Get specific variant
GET {{baseUrl}}/items/1/variants/1

### Update variant
PUT {{baseUrl}}/items/1/variants/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Variant Name",
  "price": 21.99
}

### Check if variant is in stock
GET {{baseUrl}}/items/1/variants/1/in-stock

### Reserve variant stock
POST {{baseUrl}}/items/1/variants/1/reserve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 5
}

### Release reserved variant stock
POST {{baseUrl}}/items/1/variants/1/release-reserved
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 2
}

### Deduct variant stock
POST {{baseUrl}}/items/1/variants/1/deduct
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 2
}

### Add variant stock
POST {{baseUrl}}/items/1/variants/1/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 15
}

### Delete variant
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/items/1/variants/1

### ==================== STOCK MANAGEMENT ENDPOINTS ====================

### Get all stocks
GET {{baseUrl}}/stocks

### Get stock by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/stocks/1

### Get stock for a specific item
GET {{baseUrl}}/stocks/item/1

### Update stock details
PUT {{baseUrl}}/stocks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 200,
  "reorderLevel": 30
}

### Get low stock items (items below reorder level)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stocks/alerts/low-stock

### Get out of stock items (items with zero available quantity)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stocks/alerts/out-of-stock

### ==================== VARIANT STOCK ENDPOINTS ====================

### Get all variant stocks
GET {{baseUrl}}/variant-stocks

### Get variant stock by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/variant-stocks/1

### Get stock for a specific variant
GET {{baseUrl}}/variant-stocks/variant/1

### Update variant stock details
PUT {{baseUrl}}/variant-stocks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 100,
  "reorderLevel": 15
}

### Get low stock variants
GET {{baseUrl}}/variant-stocks/alerts/low-stock

### Get out of stock variants
GET {{baseUrl}}/variant-stocks/alerts/out-of-stock

### ==================== WORKFLOW EXAMPLES ====================

### Example 1: Complete Order Fulfillment Workflow

### Step 1: Check if item is in stock
GET {{baseUrl}}/items/1/in-stock

### Step 2: Reserve stock for the order
POST {{baseUrl}}/items/1/reserve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 5
}

### Step 3: Check current stock details
GET {{baseUrl}}/stocks/item/1

### Step 4: Deduct stock when order is confirmed
POST {{baseUrl}}/items/1/deduct
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 5
}

### Example 2: Handle Order Cancellation

### Step 1: Release the reserved stock
POST {{baseUrl}}/items/1/release-reserved
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 5
}

### Example 3: Receive New Shipment

### Step 1: Check current stock
GET {{baseUrl}}/stocks/item/1

### Step 2: Add new stock
POST {{baseUrl}}/items/1/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 100
}

### Step 3: Verify new stock level
GET {{baseUrl}}/stocks/item/1

### Example 4: Monitor Low Stock Items

### Get all items that are running low on stock
GET {{baseUrl}}/stocks/alerts/low-stock

### Get all out of stock items
GET {{baseUrl}}/stocks/alerts/out-of-stock

